CatDescriptText: Bartender Tom West was murdered in Crawford Grill after refusing to serve a customer after hours. The Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, ran an article about the incident on Saturday, July 27, 1946.
TitMainTitle: Six men including "Hungry" Bill, Fonse Moore, Gus Greenlee third from left, possibly Charles "Teenie" Harris on right end, and bartender Tom West, at Crawford Grill No. 1
